Class Enquiries

java.lang.Object
models.Messages
models.Enquiries
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Messages>
public class Enquiries extends Messages
This class represents an enquiry in the system, extending the Messages class. Each enquiry has a unique identifier, a message, a sender, a camp associated with it, a helper who responds to the enquiry, and a reply.
